Terrorsaur:



Terrorsaur turned his head and nodded to Tarantulas. He turned his 
head back to Drill Bit, who sounded naive enough to be annoyed with 
going with Tarantulas. How stupid. The whole group was weakened and 
full of fools, so all he could do was tell him to go, like a newborn? 
The sense of the Predacons were fading. He rolled his eyes.

He saw Cave-In still lying on the ground. She was newborn, needing 
guidance. He hopped over and grabbed her shoulders with his claws. He 
lifted himself into the air, flapping his wings to hover.

He was ready to go.
